          "en": "My father (may God have mercy on him) narrated to us. He said: Sa'd ibn 'Abdullah ibn Abi Khalaf narrated to us. He said: Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn 'Isa narrated to me, from his father, from Muhammad ibn Abi 'Umayr, from Hammad ibn 'Uthman. He said:",
